Package edu.ncsu.csc216.packdoption.model.animals

Class Animal

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.packdoption.model.animals.Animal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Animal>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Cat, Dog
public abstract class Animal extends Object implements Comparable<Animal>
Animal class is an abstract class used to create an animal object, superclass to Cat and Dog. Animal object characteristics are different depending on if they have been adopted.
Author:
Max Farthing, David Soliman
